data.description: AMAZING views and a rare opportunity to purchase one of the most unique homes in the area! Watch the sun set and the moon rise from the huge outdoor deck overlooking the city and El Malpais, Sandstone Bluffs and Gallo Peak. The view from the covered courtyard is just as incredible with Mt Taylor being the focal point. It also has a built-in rotisserie grill. The gorgeous 900sf sunroom features a stunning Chimayo stone fireplace, viga & latilla ceiling and custom wet bar. All 4 bedrooms are of a generous size, with the primary bedroom having 2 walk-in closets, a Kiva fireplace, and that great western view! There is an eat-in area and a ton of cabinet space in the kitchen. A working dry sauna in the laundry and 3rd bath area. A great investment property - this home needs some repairs and updates but is live-in ready. Plenty of opportunity for increased equity and your own personal style! Indoor and outdoor living opportunities like this are limited! New HVAC System August 2023!
